summary.notes: All pages in this batch are FALSE_POSITIVE. Pages 203-209 are endnotes/references with proper academic citation formatting. Pages 210-219 are index pages with proper names, foreign terms, and technical vocabulary. Pages 220-225 are bibliography pages listing academic publications. The error rate flags were triggered by: (1) page number encoding artifacts (uf731, uf738, etc.), (2) foreign language terms (German, French, Latin), (3) proper nouns from multiple languages, (4) specialized academic vocabulary, and (5) footnote reference markers. None of the pages contain actual garbled English or OCR errors in the substantive text content.
